sentences.en: Dark matter: this generally refers to "exotic" non-baryonic matter that interacts only weakly with ordinary matter.
sentences.cn: 暗物质 ：这一般是指“外来的”非重子物质，与普通物质只有较弱的的相互作用。

sentences.en: Small as the percentage might be, half of the ordinary baryonic matter is unaccounted for.
sentences.cn: 这可能是个很小的百分比，有一半的普通重子物质还没有考虑到。

trans.tran_en: of or relating to a baryon
